span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">C&aacute;c phương thức thanh to&aacute;n bằng Tiền mặt &rarr; Số dư Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Thanh to&aacute;n bằng </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">Tiền T&iacute;ch Lũy / </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">C-Card</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"> </span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&rarr; Tiền T&iacute;ch Lũy / C-Card.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Thanh to&aacute;n bằng Thẻ &rarr; Thẻ.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\'\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Thanh to&aacute;n bằng Voucher/Coupon &rarr; Voucher/Coupon (chỉ &aacute;p dụng trong trường hợp thực hiện theo Ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch Trả sản phẩm).</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'policy', 1, 2, '2021-10-19 04:54:16', '2021-10-19 07:00:13');
